    skos:prefLabel "the customer's chief architect's 30-Second Pitch" ;
    rdf:value "An AI tool that extracts undocumented knowledge from senior members of staff in a conversational way, stores that as memories, and then everybody else can query it. So it's like being able to talk to those people without actually bothering them." ;
    skos:note "How an enterprise buyer describes the value: not product category but what it does—extract senior knowledge so juniors can query it without interrupting experts." .

