    skos:prefLabel "Premise Mismatch for Enterprise" ;
    rdf:value "The premise that knowledge is locked in individual AI instances doesn't match enterprise reality. Knowledge is locked in people's heads, not AI conversations." ;
    skos:note "Enterprise AI adoption is uneven; the 'AI memory lock-in' framing doesn't resonate because knowledge hasn't been externalized to AI yet." .

